  with explicit em-dash separator (decorative, aria-hidden so screen
  readers read "FileMayor by Chevza" without the hyphenation).
- Nav link order updated: Run, Triad, Doctrine, Pricing, Docs.
  Surfaces dropped from primary nav (still on the page).

